b9efe2-11d6-4690-b083-4058fbb50378.jpg\",\"https://apifranchise.mindconsulting.com.br/uploads/franchises/885606f2-8a8c-4368-b6d2-2f866777b14b.jpg\"]', 1, NULL, 0, 0, 'MAINTAIN', 0, 0, NULL, '35000', NULL, NULL, NULL, '20000', NULL, '9', '1', '10000', '5000', 12);
